steps to follow for running .php file
 1)download and extract the zip file into /xampp or lampp folder ->htdocs ->extract here.
 2)in browser at adress bar enter link localhost/filename/WP6.php and fill form
Steps to follow for sql :
1)Create a database named Assignment in phpmyadmin. OR Replace the $db assignment in Config.php with your database name.
2)select the database in phpmyadmin import the Data.sql file.

 
